msgid ""
"Number of layers to prefetch ahead of the compute frontier. Higher values"
" improve overlap at the cost of memory."
msgstr "在计算前沿之前预取的层数。更高的值可改善重叠，但会消耗更多内存。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "`layerwise_max_transfer_blocks`"
msgstr "`layerwise_max_transfer_blocks`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "`0` (unlimited)"
msgstr "`0`（无限制）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "Maximum number of KV blocks per transfer batch."
msgstr "每个传输批次的KV块最大数量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "`layerwise_max_transfer_bytes`"
msgstr "`layerwise_max_transfer_bytes`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "Maximum bytes per transfer batch."
msgstr "每个传输批次的最大字节数。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "`h2d_stagger_us`"
msgstr "`h2d_stagger_us`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "`0`"
msgstr "`0`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Stagger delay (microseconds) between H2D copies across TP ranks to avoid "
"bus contention."
msgstr "TP ranks之间H2D拷贝的错开延迟（微秒），以避免总线争用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "`discard_partial_chunks`"
msgstr "`discard_partial_chunks`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid "`true` (non-layerwise) / `false` (layerwise)"
msgstr "`true`（非逐层）/ `false`（逐层）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Whether to discard KV for incomplete chunk boundaries. Layerwise defaults"
" to `false` to preserve partial layers."
msgstr "是否丢弃不完整块边界的KV。逐层模式默认为`false`以保留部分层。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:86
msgid "Usage Scenarios"
msgstr "使用场景"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:88
msgid "PD-Mixed (kv_both)"
msgstr "PD混合（kv_both）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:90
msgid ""
"A single vLLM instance acts as both producer and consumer. The pool "
"serves as a shared prefix cache: completed requests' KV is saved layer by"
" layer, and new requests with overlapping prefixes load KV layer by "
"layer. No proxy is needed."
msgstr ""
"单个vLLM实例同时充当生产者和消费者。池作为共享前缀缓存：已完成请求的KV逐层保存，"
"具有重叠前缀的新请求逐层加载KV。无需代理。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:117
msgid "Send requests directly to port 8100 — no proxy required."
msgstr "直接向端口8100发送请求——无需代理。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:119
msgid "PD Disaggregation (kv_producer + kv_consumer)"
msgstr "PD分离（kv_producer + kv_consumer）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:121
msgid ""
"Separate prefiller and decoder instances. The prefiller saves KV layer by"
" layer; the decoder loads it layer by layer. A layerwise proxy "
"coordinates request routing and per-layer KV placement via its "
"`/v1/metaserver` endpoint."
msgstr ""
"独立的预填充和解码器实例。预填充器逐层保存KV；解码器逐层加载KV。"
"逐层代理通过其`/v1/metaserver`端点协调请求路由和逐层KV放置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:125
msgid "**Prefiller:**"
msgstr "**预填充器：**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:148
msgid "**Decoder:**"
msgstr "**解码器：**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:171
msgid ""
"**Layerwise proxy** (different from the standard disagg proxy — serves "
"`/v1/metaserver`):"
msgstr ""
"**逐层代理**（与标准分离代理不同——提供`/v1/metaserver`服务）："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:184
msgid ""
"**Note:** The proxy `--host` must **not** be `0.0.0.0` (wildcard). The "
"decoder connects back to `host:port/v1/metaserver`, so use a reachable "
"IP."
msgstr ""
"**注意：** 代理`--host`**不能**是`0.0.0.0`（通配符）。"
"解码器会回连到`host:port/v1/metaserver`，因此请使用可访问的IP。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:187
msgid "Send requests to the proxy:"
msgstr "向代理发送请求："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:200
msgid "Tuning"
msgstr "调优"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:202
msgid "Prefetch Depth"
msgstr "预取深度"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:204
msgid ""
"Increase `layerwise_prefetch_layers` (default `1`) to prefetch more "
"layers ahead of the compute frontier. This increases transfer/compute "
"overlap but uses more temporary buffers. Typical values: `1–4`."
msgstr ""
"增加`layerwise_prefetch_layers`（默认`1`）以在计算前沿之前预取更多层。"
"这增加了传输/计算重叠，但会使用更多临时缓冲区。典型值：`1–4`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:208
msgid "Transfer Batching"
msgstr "传输批处理"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:210
msgid ""
"Use `layerwise_max_transfer_blocks` or `layerwise_max_transfer_bytes` to "
"limit the size of each transfer batch. This prevents a single large layer"
" from monopolizing the transfer bus. Set to `0` (default) for unlimited."
msgstr ""
"使用`layerwise_max_transfer_blocks`或`layerwise_max_transfer_bytes`限制每个传输批次的大小。"
"这可以防止单个大层独占传输总线。设置为`0`（默认）表示无限制。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:214
msgid "H2D Stagger"
msgstr "H2D错开"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:216
msgid ""
"On multi-TP deployments, H2D (host-to-device) copies for all TP ranks can"
" contend on the PCIe/HCCS bus. Set `h2d_stagger_us` to spread them out "
"(e.g. `100` for a 100 µs stagger between ranks)."
msgstr ""
"在多TP部署中，所有TP ranks的H2D（主机到设备）拷贝可能会争用PCIe/HCCS总线。"
"设置`h2d_stagger_us`以分散它们（例如`100`表示ranks之间错开100微秒）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:220
msgid "Supported Models"
msgstr "支持的模型"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:222
msgid ""
"Layerwise mode integrates with the **MLA** (`mla_v1`) and **SFA** "
"(`sfa_v1`) attention backends. DeepSeek-V2/V3 and other MLA-based models "
"are supported."
msgstr ""
"逐层模式与**MLA**（`mla_v1`）和**SFA**（`sfa_v1`）注意力后端集成。"
"支持DeepSeek-V2/V3和其他基于MLA的模型。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:225
msgid ""
"Basic full attention (`attention_v1`) and all context-parallel (CP) "
"variants (`mla_cp`, `sfa_cp`, `attention_cp`) do **not** yet integrate "
"the layerwise wait/save calls. Layerwise + CP is future work."
msgstr ""
"基本全注意力（`attention_v1`）和所有上下文并行（CP）变体（`mla_cp`、`sfa_cp`、`attention_cp`）**
尚未**集成逐层等待/保存调用。逐层+CP是未来工作。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:229
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr "限制"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:231
msgid ""
"**Backend**: Only `memcache` is supported for layerwise mode (`mooncake` "
"and `yuanrong` do not support `use_layerwise`)."
msgstr ""
"**后端**：逐层模式仅支持`memcache`（`mooncake`和`yuanrong`不支持`use_layerwise`）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:233
msgid ""
"**Hybrid KV cache**: Not supported — layerwise raises "
"`NotImplementedError` when the model has multiple KV cache group families"
" (hybrid MLA + sliding-window attention)."
msgstr ""
"**混合KV缓存**：不支持——当模型有多个KV缓存组族（混合MLA+滑动窗口注意力）时，"
"逐层模式会抛出`NotImplementedError`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:236
msgid ""
"**Context parallel**: Layerwise is not yet integrated with CP attention "
"backends."
msgstr "**上下文并行**：逐层模式尚未与CP注意力后端集成。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/layerwise_kv_pool.md:238
msgid ""
"**PD disaggregation proxy**: When using `kv_producer` / `kv_consumer`, "
"the dedicated layerwise proxy "
"(`load_balance_proxy_layerwise_server_example.py`) is required — the "
"standard disagg proxy does not serve the `/v1/metaserver` endpoint."
msgstr ""
"**PD分离代理**：使用`kv_producer` / `kv_consumer`时，需要专用的逐层代理"
"（`load_balance_proxy_layerwise_server_example.py`）——标准分离代理不提供`/v1/metaserver`端点。"